Purpose of the class: Represents a patient in a specific study in a specific clinical site. The patient has a unique TrialDB number.

public int getTodayAgeYears()

addDecision

public void addDecision(ClinicalDecision decision)
This procedure fills in decision information related to the current state of the patient. This is done because a decision may be made with patient data that are different, whether because of a correction, or simply because the patient is older or has changed weight or height.

Parameters:
